```mermaid

graph TD
  A[User] --> B[Frontend - Next.js]

  B --> C[POST /api/login]

  C --> D[Validate input]

  D --> E[Authenticate user]

  E --> |Success| F[Generate JWT\nRefreshToken.for_user]
  E --> |Fail| G[Return error]

  F --> H[Return access + refresh token]

  H --> I[Frontend stores token]

  I --> J[Subsequent request] 

  J --> K[Authorization: Bearer <token>]

  K --> L[Backend verifies token]

  L --> |Success| M[Return 200 User authenticated]

  L --> |Fail| U[Return 401 Unauthorized]